---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Investment Strategies | Financial Management"
  description="Learn about investment strategies tailored for UK veterans receiving compensation through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Understand how to grow and protect your financial assets.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Investment Strategies for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">Managing and investing compensation received through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) can help secure your financial future. This page outlines various investment strategies and considerations tailored to the needs of veterans.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Understanding Your Financial Goals</h2>
        <p>Before investing, consider your financial objectives:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Short-term needs vs. long-term financial security</li>
          <li>Retirement planning</li>
          <li>Providing for family members</li>
          <li>Funding further education or career transition</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Types of Investments</h2>
        <p>Various investment options to consider:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Stocks and shares</li>
          <li>Bonds and gilts</li>
          <li>Property investments</li>
          <li>Mutual funds and ETFs</li>
          <li>Savings accounts and Cash ISAs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Risk Assessment</h2>
        <p>Understanding and managing investment risk:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assessing your risk tolerance</li>
          <li>Balancing risk and potential returns</li>
          <li>Diversification strategies</li>
          <li>Regular review and rebalancing of your portfolio</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Tax-Efficient Investing</h2>
        <p>Maximising your investments through tax-efficient methods:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Utilising ISA allowances</li>
          <li>Understanding the tax implications of different investment types</li>
          <li>Considering pension contributions for tax relief</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Long-Term Investment Strategies</h2>
        <p>Approaches for long-term financial growth:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Dollar-cost averaging</li>
          <li>Compound interest and reinvestment</li>
          <li>Asset allocation based on age and retirement goals</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Seeking Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>The benefits of professional financial guidance:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Working with financial advisors experienced in veteran affairs</li>
          <li>Regular financial health check-ups</li>
          <li>Adapting your investment strategy as your circumstances change</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/financial/pension-planning" class="text-decoration-none">Pension Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/tax-benefits" class="text-decoration-none">Tax Benefits</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/financial-advice" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Advice Services</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Investment Planning Session</h3>
            <p>Book a one-on-one session with our financial advisors to create a personalised investment strategy.</p>
            <a href="/investment-planning" class="btn btn-primary">Book Session</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
